data.description: Welcome to your new home!! This Beautiful 6 year old home comes with a patio, deck with a metal gazebo and attached built in garage. As you walk in the front door you'll notice a spacious open concept family room and kitchen with an island perfect for cooking and entertaining with a first floor office right off the garage entrance. It also boasts a 2nd floor laundry room and two full bathrooms along with 4 bedrooms! Don't miss out on this opportunity to own this beautiful home that also comes equipped with a HOME WARRANTY!!
